to the two Americans.

01:00.920 --> 01:03.320
[theme music playing]

01:37.280 --> 01:39.320
[marching band playing]

01:48.840 --> 01:51.320
We gotta move fast.
They got Jonas.

01:51.400 --> 01:53.640
- What? Who?
- The two Americans we've been chasing.

01:53.720 --> 01:56.640
Look what I found in the street.
They got him.

01:56.720 --> 01:59.280
[in Norwegian] But who are these people?
What do they want with us?

01:59.360 --> 02:02.080
[in English] The only question
that matters is, how do we find them?

02:02.160 --> 02:03.800
Now, just think.

02:07.040 --> 02:10.120
You know Olympia?

02:10.200 --> 02:11.760
[in English]
Julius' daughter?

02:11.840 --> 02:13.840
[in Norwegian]
I think she was on the grad party bus.

02:13.920 --> 02:17.160
Maybe she knows
where they met the Americans.

02:17.240 --> 02:18.520
[in English] Good thinkin'.

02:18.600 --> 02:20.400
[camera clicks]

02:27.360 --> 02:31.400
[in Norwegian] Hi. There you are.
Did you find Jonas?

02:31.480 --> 02:33.800
[in English] Yeah. He went to hang out
with some friends.

02:33.880 --> 02:35.320
[in Norwegian] Oh, who?

02:35.400 --> 02:38.800
