and some other pals.

02:38.880 --> 02:42.320
You know, went to the school
to play some games.

02:42.400 --> 02:44.960
But our distributor called
and we got to run.

02:45.040 --> 02:46.880
[in Norwegian]
Now? It's the National Day.

02:46.960 --> 02:48.800
[in English] I know, I know.
Really, it's terrible.

02:48.880 --> 02:50.120
[in Norwegian]
No. You can't leave now.

02:50.200 --> 02:51.640
[in English]
Be back later, okay?

02:51.720 --> 02:53.160
[in Norwegian]   It's the National Day.
You can't just leave.

02:53.240 --> 02:54.280
[Johnny] Okay.

02:57.000 --> 03:01.720
[Sigrid in Norwegian] Johnny had to do
some work. Dear me.

03:01.800 --> 03:05.320
