that it'll be like up at the cabin.

03:16.800 --> 03:17.720
No.

03:17.800 --> 03:20.040
I've gone over to fruit juice now.

03:20.120 --> 03:24.040
I wasn't thinking of that.
I just lost my energy.

03:24.120 --> 03:25.840
Come with me.

03:27.360 --> 03:31.040
Lots of exciting people
of all colors and shapes.

03:33.800 --> 03:35.720
Yes, maybe just a short visit.

03:35.800 --> 03:37.640
Yes, come.

03:38.760 --> 03:41.320
- It'll be great.
- I don't know Reidun.

03:41.400 --> 03:43.160
Yes, you do.

03:52.400 --> 03:55.520
[in English]
Why did you stop the car?

03:55.600 --> 03:58.240
[in Norwegian] You know
I back you up all the way, boss.

03:59.240 --> 04:00.760
[in English] Yeah.

04:00.840 --> 04:05.800
