let's go get the kid.

05:16.360 --> 05:19.080
You got it, Agent Henriksen.

05:23.600 --> 05:25.200
[clinking glass]

05:26.160 --> 05:28.840
[in Norwegian]
Yes...

05:28.920 --> 05:35.080
As most of you know, this has been
a tough year for the Backe family.

05:35.160 --> 05:38.120
